data.description:
Welcome to this stunning 3+ bedroom, 3-bathroom oasis nestled on a beautifully landscaped property adorned with lush trees and boasting a refreshing pool, offering the perfect balance of luxury, comfort, and versatility. 

Upon arriving, you'll be impressed by the charming curb appeal and inviting entrance of this spacious 2,920 square feet home. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed layout, blending contemporary elegance with functional living spaces.

The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, ample granite countertops with bar area, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests. The adjacent dining area overlooks the pool and outdoor living spaces, creating a seamless connection between indoors and outdoors.

The heart of the home is the two open concept living rooms. One with a cozy feel featuring a gas fireplace and one bathed in natural light, courtesy of large windows and glass doors that lead to the poolside retreat. 

One of the unique features of this home is the flex space, providing endless possibilities to adapt the room to suit your lifestyle. Whether it becomes a home office, a fitness center, a media room, a playroom for the little ones, or a 4th bedroom. The choice is yours.

Step outside to your own private paradise, where a sparkling pool awaits, inviting you to take a refreshing dip on warm days. The spacious patio and outdoor lounge area provide an idyllic setting for dining, entertaining, or simply enjoying your morning coffee. The property's mature trees offer shade and privacy, creating a tranquil retreat right in your backyard. 

Conveniently located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home offers easy access to schools, parks, shopping, and dining. With its combination of modern comforts, flexible living spaces, and serene outdoor amenities, this property is a true gem that promises an exceptional living experience for you and your family. The recent updates and small detailed touch ups are worth seeing!
